        },
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "describing",
          "value": "Mathlib has no dedicated `IVP` structure; an IVP is expressed via the pattern `α t₀ = y₀ ∧ ∀ t, HasDerivAt α (f t (α t)) t` (as in the conclusion of `exists_eq_forall_mem_Icc_hasDerivWithinAt`).",
          "format": "text/plain"
        }
      ],
      "target": {
        "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Picard%E2%80%93Lindel%C3%B6f_theorem?oldid=1346301030",
        "selector": {
