          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "describing",
          "value": "Mathlib proves that some iterate `(next hf hx)^[n]` is a `ContractingWith C`, which suffices to apply Banach fixed-point and is strictly more general than directly contracting Γ.",
          "format": "text/plain"
        }
      ],
